reviewText: I already owned the audio but to hear it live it's a whole new experience. It is worth getting to know Manu on a whole new level through the short documentaries. A must have!

For Manu Chao fans, this DVD is awesome. Recorded in 2002, it highlights Chao with his band Radio Bemba Sound System. Includes footage edited from two live concerts, a tour documentary and another documentary that is edited with lots of music and artwork. Highly recommend for new and current fans of Seor Chao. Pris ses nuits!  Esperanza!
O DVD chegou ao Brasil com 2 semanas de antecedncia em relao ao prazo previsto pelo site e em perfeito estado!
